description:
The beast has been walking through girls in in Summer Vengeance. It would appear, she has pick up the spirt of the site. She had a wrestling back ground, she just needed to figure out how to molest girls WHILE she wrestled and it looks like she's learned a thing or two.
La Diabla is a beast of her own. She been mopping the floor with girls. This match is competitive back and forth action but one reigns supreme in the end and moves on in the tournament.
title: The Beast meets La Diabla in on Hell of a Match
